                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_9" name="selection_3" value="3")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_9" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10") I don´t know.

                    div(class="row mb50")
                        p • Her mother is taking her to the zoo.
                        div(class="row-flex")
